    <summary>Specifies the arguments used to clone a typeface with custom variation axis positions and palette settings.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontArguments` specifies the parameters used to clone a typeface with
custom variation axis positions, palette selection, and palette color overrides.
Pass an instance to <xref:SkiaSharp.SKTypeface.Clone(SkiaSharp.SKFontArguments)>
to obtain a new typeface configured with the given arguments.

This is a `ref struct` and cannot be stored on the heap.

## Examples

```csharp
var args = new SKFontArguments
{
    CollectionIndex = 0,
    PaletteIndex = 1,
};
using var variant = typeface.Clone(args);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
